name: The Hanging Shit, from the series "Delicate Protests"
description:
This image's purpose is not to be offensive in any way but to illustrate a serious feeling and a movement. The "Delicate Protests" Series brings photos of real-life situations made by frustrated people in funny ways.

Note: We are new to the site, if it's against the rules by any means we are profoundly sorry and agree to remove it from the site.
